        {
            "title": "荃灣果茶店「檸季」遭淋紅油  警追緝1男歹徒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"荃灣果茶店「檸季」遭淋紅油  警追緝1男歹徒。網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d50fa2d216d8ee95739f3e0d72455073/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040403320037069.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">荃灣果茶店「檸季」遭淋紅油  警追緝1男歹徒。網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣發生刑毀案。周五（4日）凌晨1時許，楊屋道1號荃新天地商場內，一間名為「檸季」的果茶店遭淋紅油，店面牆壁和地面被污損，商場保安發現報警。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，警員經初步調查，懷疑涉案人為一名男子，正追查其下落。案件列「刑毀」跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176117/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/737868d171fc8d6fbe5ac2cbb976b852/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-03_at_8_15_27_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062045/即時-港聞-荃灣果茶店-檸季-遭淋紅油-警追緝1男歹徒",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-04 03:46:21",
