            "title": "44歲肌肉男星驚傳猝逝　跑步機上突然身亡  年幼妻兒孤苦無依",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"44歲肌肉男星驚傳猝逝　跑步機上突然身亡  年幼妻兒孤苦無依\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b46a810e101e1faab0c29db4beb45e20/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040322071368173.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">44歲肌肉男星驚傳猝逝　跑步機上突然身亡  年幼妻兒孤苦無依</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>伊朗男星維托里奧皮爾巴扎里（Vittorio Pirbazari）曾演出Netflix影集《柏林犬》、《犯罪現場》，在歐美小有知名度，一身壯碩肌肉以及樂觀性格讓他在網路上也有不少支持者，近期卻傳出在跑步機上訓練時，竟不幸猝逝，享年44歲。維托里奧的導演好友賽義德易卜拉欣（Said Ibrahim）也在IG上證實此事，「你永遠不知道什麼時候會發生！因為一切都只是一瞬間的事。」\n\n</p><h2>剛結束新電影拍攝</h2>\n<p>維托里奧才剛結束新電影《Haps-Crime Doesn\\'t Pay》的拍攝，該片也成為他的遺作，電影官方IG專頁上也發文悼念：「團隊對於維托里奧皮爾巴扎里的去世深感哀悼，我們的心與他的家人同在，感謝你的溫暖、你的創造精神，感謝你成為我們旅程的一部分。我們將懷念你，願你安息！」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3443572/%E4%B8%89%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%A8%E5%8D%93%E8%BA%922%E6%9C%88%E5%88%9D%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96%E9%81%BA%E4%BD%9C%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA-%E6%BC%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%BC%89%E9%A7%B1%E6%BE%A4%E4%BF%A1%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E7%94%9F%E4%BB%94-%E9%98%AE%E5%BE%B7%E9%8F%98%E4%BC%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%82%A8%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%8C%E5%89%8D%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD\">三命丨卓躒2月初離世遺作播出 演好心司機載「駱澤信媽媽」生仔 阮德鏘：估不到在您生忌前首播</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175989/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Vittorio Pirbazari不幸離世。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f66a471f1af8362f4185c8f7e395f75/2025-04/rr1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Vittorio Pirbazari不幸離世。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175990/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Vittorio Pirbazari驟逝遺下妻兒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33067ddae43d8513580739ca6be4b0c2/2025-04/rr2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Vittorio Pirbazari驟逝遺下妻兒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>死於心臟病發</h2>\n<p>遺憾的是，維托里奧甚至才剛結束電影首映，就在3月31日傳出驟逝的消息，死因是在跑步機上訓練時心臟病發。維托里奧離世後，僅留下了妻子和4歲兒子。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/health-care/3443443/65%E6%AD%B2%E9%9F%8B%E5%9F%BA%E9%A6%ACVal-Kilmer%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E6%9B%BE%E6%82%A3%E5%96%89%E7%99%8C%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%B2-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%836%E5%A4%A7%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80-%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E8%81%B2%E6%B2%99%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E8%99%9F\">65歲韋基馬Val Kilmer離世 曾患喉癌永久失聲 小心6大症狀 持續聲沙是警號</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062029/即時-娛樂-44歲肌肉男星驚傳猝逝-跑步機上突然身亡-年幼妻兒孤苦無依",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 23:16:20",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
